#### üé≤ Best "Board Game Cafe" Hack: 2nd Place ü•à

![Image](https://i.imgur.com/bVAUlbn.png)

**Team:** Team Pineapple aka @Jef üá∫üá∏, @mayonnaise üá®üá¶, @Rhea_K üá∫üá∏
**Submission:** https://www.codedex.io/community/hackathon/V6EKtYm8vKQEVLCVcGGy
**Website:** https://sipnplay.vercel.app/
**Tools:** React, Tailwind CSS, Three.js, Leaflet Map, Vercel
**Prize:** One AirPods Pro (2nd gen) per team member

The web app helps people create and store their New Year resolutions, generate new ones, and also provides a countdown timer to 2024. This team built and deployed the web app on Vercel in just 12 hours ‚Äî it was the fastest submission and overall just rock solid. Incredible job, Sebastian and James!

